簡單的繪圖（ggplot2)

a. 散佈圖

library(ggplot2)
ggplot(Orange, aes(x = age, y = circumference)) +
geom_point() +  
ggtitle("Age vs. Circumference") +
xlab("Age") +
ylab("Circumference") +
geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = F)

b. 線圖

ggplot(BOD, aes(x = Time, y = demand)) +
  geom_line() +
  ggtitle("Biochemical Oxygen Demand")

c. 直方圖

ggplot(LifeCycleSavings, aes(x = sr)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 5)

d. 盒鬚圖

ggplot(iris, aes(x = Species, y = Sepal.Length)) +
  geom_boxplot(fill = "black", colour = "white")

e. 長條圖

ggplot(mtcars, aes(x = row.names(mtcars), y = hp)) +
geom_bar(stat = "identity") +
theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90, hjust = 1, vjust = 0, size = 8))
